=========
Norge Postnummer

=========
Data update policy
==================

No changes to the data will be accepted into norgepostnummer.

Build status
============

Norge Postnummer
====================

Post numbers are accessible through a database object that is already configured
upon import of norgepostnummer and works as an iterable:

  >>> import norgepostnummer
  >>> len(norgepostnummer.steder)
  >>> list(norgepostnummer.steder)[0]
